Description:
    Generates a new controller and routes for use with CafeCar.

    Pass --skip-routes to generate only the controller.

Example:
    bin/rails generate cafe_car:controller admin/invoices

    This creates:
        app/controllers/admin/invoices_controller.rb

    It also adds `resources :invoices` inside `namespace :admin` in
    config/routes.rb. Pass --skip-routes when the route already exists.
